      "zh": "你是我唯一的人。",
      "ja": "あなたは私のただ一人。",
      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're my only one.",
      "zh": "你是我唯一的人。",
      "ja": "あなたは私のただ一人。",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're my last breath.",
      "zh": "你是我最後的呼吸。",
      "ja": "あなたは私の最後の息。",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're home.",
      "zh": "你是我的家。",
      "ja": "あなたは私の家。",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No goodbye.",
      "zh": "沒有告別。",
      "ja": "さよならはない。",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Love has grown.",
      "zh": "愛已成長。",
      "ja": "愛は育った。",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're my only one.",
